company overview: Business: Financial service provider, licensed by the Nigerian Stock Exchange (NSE) and the Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) as a Broker/Dealer.

Stated Philosophy/Mission: "Understand that excellent service and professionalism distinguish results from extraordinary results. We attach great importance to quality delivery of life-changing products and services to all our clients and customers with strong emphasis on excellent customer satisfaction." Aims to be "always ahead" and provide "Professional Solutions for Your Business."
Year of Operation Implied: Website copyright ©2020.
Website Developer: "Designed and Developed by Skyview Capital IT."
services offered by skyview capital limi: Clientele: Government parastatals, multinational and indigenous companies, high net worth individuals.
Supported by: "Seasoned professional researchers" for stock analysis.
Sub-services: Retainer-ship for listed companies, Certificate Verification (phasing out), Receiving Agency for IPOs/POs.
Report types mentioned: Skyview Research Report, Weekly, Monthly, Quarterly, Annual Reports.
Utilizes in-house researchers for daily securities updates for clients.
Employs tools for valuing assets, debts, warrants, and equity using public information/financial statements.
